class Sink[-A]                          // contravariant
class Handler[A](default: A)           // invariant
```

## Option Instead of Null
- `Option[A]` = `Some(value)` or `None`
- Use `.map`, `.flatMap`, `.getOrElse`, `.fold` for safe access
- Never use `null` in idiomatic Scala

